### Authorization by token, part 1. Retrieve and save token.

### Proceso de Login de un Admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "User1"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}

### Proceso de Login de un Usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "steam",
  "password": "Test1"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}


### Authorization by token, part 2. Use token to authorize.

### Debería funcionar con rol USER
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Debería funcionar con user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/me/videojuegos
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Debería fallar con user porque no tiene perfil adecuado
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}